AUDIO: 'If you\'ve been seeing all the posts about Apple sharp that lets you quickly turn any 2D image into essentially a 3D photo and want to start creating with it quickly and for free, this video is for you. To get started, we\'re going to head to anaconda.org to download mini conda here and we\'re going to click in the top'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'right corner and hit mini conda for Apple silicon. And so once it\'s done, we\'re going to double click to run the installation wizard, which shouldn\'t take too long. Then we\'re just going to hit continue, continue again, continue one more time, and then agree, and then'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'we\'re going to install it directly onto the computer. And this part of actually running the package scripts might take a little bit longer for you depending on your device, but once it finishes, we are then going to just quickly close it and move on to the next step. So to do'

